    • Field Detail

      • ISPN_CONFIG_FILE

        public static final String ISPN_CONFIG_FILE
        This optional parameter specifies the location of the XML file used to configure Infinispan. This file should be available in the application's classpath. This can be set via FenixFramework config file by prefixing it with JvstmLockFreeConfig.DATAGRID_PARAM_PREFIX.
